compat-change.description: Wear products currently force a slight scaling transition to wallpapers when the QSS is opened. However, on Wear 6 (SDK 35) and above, 1P watch faces will be expected to either implement their own scaling, or to override this method to allow the WallpaperController to continue to scale for them.
compat-change.name: WEAROS_WALLPAPER_HANDLES_SCALING
